NK106(me)005:1: // rdzogs pa chen po bsam gtan ngal gso'i bsdus don
NK106(me)005:2: pun+da r+ai ka'i phreng ba zhes bya ba bzhugs so
NK106(me)005:3: // dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK106(me)005:4: 'dir rdzogs pa chen po bsam gtan ngal gso'i gnas rgya cher bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK106(me)005:7: bstan bcos yongs su rdzogs pa'i bya ba'o //
NK106(me)005:13: brtsam par dam bca' bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)005:15: lus rnam par gzhag pa dang /
NK106(me)005:16: yan lag rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK106(me)005:18: gnas gsum bstan bcos kyi lus la 'jug par gdams pa dang /
NK106(me)005:19: 'jug yul lus kyi sdom rnam par gzhag pa'o //
NK106(me)005:20: gnyis pa yan lag rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK106(me)005:21: gang du nyams su len pa'i gnas /
NK106(me)005:22: gang gi nyams su len pa'i gang zag /
NK106(me)005:23: gang nyams su blang ba'i chos rgya cher bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)005:25: gnas kyi rim pa brtag pa /
NK106(me)005:26: spyir bsam gtan gyi khang bu bya ba bye brag tu bshad pa /
NK106(me)005:27: de gnyis ka'i don bsdu ba'o //
NK106(me)005:29: dus bzhi gnas kyi rim pa /
NK106(me)005:30: so so gnas kyi rang bzhin /
NK106(me)005:31: las bzhi gnas kyi khyad par bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)005:35: dpyid kyi rgyas par bshad don bsdu ba'o //
NK106(me)005:37: so so'i bye brag bstan pa dang /
NK106(me)005:38: blang dor gyi dmigs dbye ba'o //
NK106(me)005:39: dang po la bcu gcig ste /
NK106(me)005:50: mtsho 'gram gyi rang bzhin bsten pas nang gi sems kyi 'char tshul bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)005:51: gnyis pa blang dor gyi dmigs dbye ba la gsum ste /
NK106(me)005:55: gsum pa la gzhi gnas kyi khyad par la gsum ste /
NK106(me)005:56: gnas brtag pa'i dgos ched la spyir gdams pa /
NK106(me)005:57: zhi rgyas dbang drag bzhi bye brag tu bshad pa /
NK106(me)005:58: skabs kyi don ngos gzung ba'o //
NK106(me)005:59: gnyis pa la bsam gtan gyi khang bu bya ba la gsum ste /
NK106(me)005:60: bsam gtan gyi khang bu spyi'i rang bzhin /
NK106(me)005:61: mtshan mo dang nyin mo rnal 'byor gyi bye brag gi rang bzhin /
NK106(me)005:64: zhi lhag so so'i sgrub dus /
NK106(me)005:65: rgyun gyi rnal 'byor gyis sgrub dus /
NK106(me)005:66: bye brag shes pas bstan pa'i nye 'khor gyi rang bzhin bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)005:67: gsum pa don bsdu ba la gsum ste /
NK106(me)005:68: bstan bya snying po byang chub kyi gnas /
NK106(me)005:69: spang bya las ngan bdud kyi gnas /
NK106(me)005:70: yid ches dgod pa lung gi gnas rgya cher bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)005:71: gnas dang po'i bsdus don no ////
NK106(me)005:72: don gnyis pa gang gis nyams su len pa'i gang zag gi gnas bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK106(me)005:73: gang zag gi gnas la spyir gdams /
NK106(me)005:74: sgrub tshul gyi gnas la bye brag tu gdams /
NK106(me)005:75: bsgrub dgos pa'i rgyu mtshan rgya cher bshad pa'o //
NK106(me)005:77: gang zag gi gdams pa'i mtshan nyid bstan pa /
NK106(me)005:78: mtshan nyid can des bsgrub par gdams pa'o //
NK106(me)005:80: gzhi rten bslab gsum la gdams pa /
NK106(me)005:81: dben par rang don la bskul ba /
NK106(me)005:83: ngo tsha khrel yod bsten pa /
NK106(me)005:84: grag stong bzod pa bsgom pa /
NK106(me)005:85: ci byed chos pa brtson par bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)005:86: gsum pa la bco lnga ste /
NK106(me)005:87: dus ngan skye bo dang 'grogs par mi bzod pa /
NK106(me)005:88: mngon shes med par gzhan don 'grub dka' ba /
NK106(me)005:89: rnam g.yeng 'du 'dzis sgrub pa bslu ba /
NK106(me)005:91: da res legs pa'i 'dun ma bsam pa /
NK106(me)005:92: phyi ma'i sa zin da lta dgos pa /
NK106(me)005:93: 'khor ba'i gnas las thar thabs dgos pa /
NK106(me)005:94: ma 'khrul don gyi btsan sa gzung ba /
NK106(me)005:95: dal 'byor gru bos srid mtsho brgal ba /
NK106(me)005:96: thar lam zhugs nas 'bad pa 'don pa /
NK106(me)005:97: skyo shas skye ba'i yul la bsam pa /
NK106(me)005:98: las kyis rlung shugs cis kyang bzlog pa /
NK106(me)005:99: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal bzod glags med par bsam pa /
NK106(me)005:100: dal khams med par brtson 'grus bskyed pa /
NK106(me)005:101: chos la bsams pa'i phan yon bstan pa /
NK106(me)005:102: thar lam bsgrub pa'i gang zag la bsams te bsgrub dgos pa'i rgyu mtshan dgod pa'o //
NK106(me)005:103: gnas gnyis pa'i bsdus don no ////
NK106(me)005:104: don gsum pa gang nyams su blang bya'i chos rgya cher bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK106(me)005:105: sgom pa mdor bstan pa dang /
NK106(me)005:106: sde tshan rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK106(me)005:118: spyi bor bla ma'i rnal 'byor bsgoms pas khyad par
NK106(me)005:119: mchog gi sngon 'gro dgos pa dang bcas pa bstan
NK106(me)005:120: pa'o // gnyis pa dngos gzhi la gnyis te /
NK106(me)005:126: mi rtog pa'i thabs la ngo sprad pa'o //
NK106(me)005:129: gtum mo'i mes byang chub kyi sems bzhu /
NK106(me)005:130: bde chen bam la sems bzung /
NK106(me)005:131: phra mo'i rnal 'byor bsgoms pa dang bzhis bde ba'i thabs bsgom pa /
NK106(me)005:132: thabs las thob pa'i 'od gsal bstan pa /
NK106(me)005:133: de las nyams kyi skye tshul bstan pa /
NK106(me)005:134: goms pas thob pa'i yon tan bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)005:135: gnyis pa gsal ba'i thabs la lnga ste /
NK106(me)005:140: rtags tshad bstan pa dang lnga gsal ba'i thabs bsgom pa /
NK106(me)005:142: ye shes dngos kyi thabs las thob pa'i 'od gsal /
NK106(me)005:143: de las nyams kyi skye tshul /
NK106(me)005:145: gsum pa mi rtog pa'i thabs lnga ste /
NK106(me)005:156: spros bral dag pas gzung ba /
NK106(me)005:160: dran bsam dag pas sbyang ba'o ////
NK106(me)005:161: don gsum pa rjes la gnyis te /
NK106(me)005:170: 'brel ba gsum gyi ngo bo spyir bstan /
NK106(me)005:173: mi rtog pa log pa gsum gyi rang bzhin bye brag tu bshad /
NK106(me)005:174: bcos thabs nges pas don bsdu ba'o //
NK106(me)005:175: gnyis pa bogs 'byin pa la gnyis te /
NK106(me)005:176: ngo bo mdor bstan pa dang /
NK106(me)005:177: rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK106(me)005:184: tha ma spyod pas bcos pa'o //
NK106(me)005:186: ye stod snyems bral du la bzla ba dang /
NK106(me)005:187: gol sgrib chos nyid kyi rol par rang shar ba'o //
NK106(me)005:189: gnad kyi ngo bo mdor bstan /
NK106(me)005:191: 'dzin med chen por don bsdu ba'o //
NK106(me)005:194: mi rtog pa'i nyams skyon can bcos pa'o //
NK106(me)005:200: rig pa dngas snyigs dbye ba /
NK106(me)005:205: rtog med dbyings su dag pa dang /
NK106(me)005:206: bying rmugs dgra bo gzhom pa'o //
NK106(me)005:207: gsum pa 'dzin med du don bsdu ba la gnyis te /
NK106(me)005:208: re dogs 'dzin pa gzhom pa dang /
NK106(me)005:209: de'i ngang la gzhag tshul lo //
NK106(me)005:210: gsum pa tha mas spyod pas bcos pa la gnyis te /
NK106(me)005:221: 'khrul 'khor gyi gnad kyis spyir bstan pa dang /
NK106(me)005:224: mi rtog pa'i lus gnad kyis bye brag gi lta stangs bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)005:225: gsum pa rten 'brel la gsum ste /
NK106(me)005:228: bying rmugs bsal ba'i rten 'brel lo //
NK106(me)005:229: gnyis pa bogs 'byin dngos la gnyis te /
NK106(me)005:232: log rtog dgag pas gnas mdor bstan pa dang /
NK106(me)005:233: so so'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK106(me)005:235: so so dang spyi'i bogs 'byin no //
NK106(me)005:241: dngas ma chos nyid kyi klong du sba ba dang /
NK106(me)005:242: rlung sems skye med kyi klong du sba bas bde chen 'od gsal gyi 'khor lo bstan pa dang /
NK106(me)005:243: chings lnga mdor bstan pa dang /
NK106(me)005:247: la bzla ba'i gnas rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK106(me)005:248: gnyis pa gsal ba'i bogs 'byin pa la lnga ste /
NK106(me)005:250: khyad par gyi gnad bye brag tu gdams /
NK106(me)005:251: gnad mchog rgyal po'i man ngag dngos bstan /
NK106(me)005:252: thabs kyi yan lag rgya cher brjod /
NK106(me)005:253: goms pas thob pa'i yon tan la basngagasa pa'o //
NK106(me)005:254: gsum pa mi rtog pa'i bogs 'byin la bzhi ste /
NK106(me)005:258: chos nyid kyi gnad bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)005:259: gnyis pa spyi'i bogs 'byin pa la gnyis te /
NK106(me)005:262: gsum pa rtogs pa la dgu ste /
NK106(me)005:263: ngo bo ris med mtha' bral /
NK106(me)005:264: dpe don thabs gsum don gcig /
NK106(me)005:265: rang bzhin bde gshegs snying po /
NK106(me)005:268: rig stong chos sku rjen pa /
NK106(me)005:269: ming don du ma ro gcig /
NK106(me)005:270: gzhi bral nam mkha' lta bu /
NK106(me)005:271: blo 'das chos zad chen por bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)005:272: bzhi pa 'bras bu la gnyis te /
NK106(me)005:275: gnas gsum pa'i bsdus don no ////
NK106(me)005:276: spyi don gsum pa bstan bcos yongs su rdzogs pa'i bya ba la lnga ste /
NK106(me)005:277: dge ba byang chub tu bsngo ba /
NK106(me)005:278: gang gis gang du brtsams pa'i tshul brjod pa la /
NK106(me)005:279: skal bzang skye bo la gdams pa /
NK106(me)005:281: yongs su rdzogs pa mtshan gyi don to //
NK106(me)005:282: rdzogs pa chen po bsam gtan ngal gso'i bsdus don pun+da r+ai ka'i phreng ba zhes bya ba /
NK106(me)005:283: thos pa dang bsam pa dang /
NK106(me)005:284: sgom pa las byung ba'i shes rab kyi blo'i pad+mo
NK106(me)005:285: 'dzum par byas pa'i rnal 'byor pa dri med 'od
NK106(me)005:286: zer gyis gangs ri thod dkar gyi mgul 'od zer
NK106(me)005:287: sprin gyi skyed mos tshal gyi nang kun tu bzang
NK106(me)005:288: po'i khang bzangs su sbyar ba'o //
